{"date":"1996-04-05","platform":"TV","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/bc/73/1515_OehG3.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/bc/73/1515_OehG3.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/bc/73/1515_OehG3.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/bc/73/1515_OehG3.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/bc/73/1515_OehG3.jpg"},"summary":"以“小孩子”的角度去探讨学级崩坏、青少年犯罪、家庭关系破裂、父母离异等现代的社会问题。作品超越了一般的少女漫画，得到社会各年代的支持。主角是一名童星，在作品发表时童星是非常备受注目的。在漫画连载初期到动漫放映初期的1996年间，童星是社会的热门话题，但到有关热潮无论在演艺界和社会上都已退却的1998年时，漫画版也连载完毕。当时有传言至如果童星热潮不减的话将会有第2部作品，但最终都没有实现。\r\n\r\n结局中由于童星热的减却，主角仓田纱南的人气也大不如前，却也同时暗示了她内心的蜕变和成长。\r\n","name":"こどものおもちゃ","name_cn":"玩偶游戏","tags":[{"name":"TV","count":77,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1996","count":75,"total_cont":0},{"name":"大地丙太郎","count":59,"total_cont":0},{"name":"漫画改","count":56,"total_cont":0},{"name":"小孩子的玩具","count":47,"total_cont":0},{"name":"童年","count":44,"total_cont":0},{"name":"恋爱","count":42,"total_cont":0},{"name":"少女向","count":34,"total_cont":0},{"name":"玩偶遊戲","count":30,"total_cont":0},{"name":"小花美穂","count":28,"total_cont":0},{"name":"羽山秋人","count":23,"total_cont":0},{"name":"仓田纱南","count":22,"total_cont":0},{"name":"漫改","count":14,"total_cont":0},{"name":"ATV","count":12,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本","count":10,"total_cont":0},{"name":"StudioGallop","count":8,"total_cont":0},{"name":"校园","count":8,"total_cont":0},{"name":"搞笑","count":8,"total_cont":0},{"name":"ぎゃろっぷ","count":7,"total_cont":0},{"name":"GALLOP","count":7,"total_cont":0},{"name":"补番","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"ATV!","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"青春","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"90年代","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"偶像","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"治愈","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"子供向","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"少女漫","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"女性向","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1990s","count":2,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"玩偶游戏"},{"key":"别名","value":[{"v":"小孩子的